PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FThe four-month-old grandson of
OL,7,Ffootball manager Steve Bruce died
OL,8,Fafter he was placed in an "unsafe
OL,9,Fsleeping position" in his cot by an
OL,10,Funregulated maternity nurse, an
OL,11,Finquest has heard.
OL,13,FThe baby, Madison Bruce Smith, was
OL,14,Ffound unresponsive by his father on
OL,15,Fthe morning of 18 October 2024.
OL,17,FThe infant could not be resuscitated
OL,18,Fat the family home in Trafford,
OL,19,FGreater Manchester, and was taken to
OL,20,FWythenshawe Hospital where he was
OL,21,Fpronounced dead by paramedics.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FMadison's parents ex-Leeds United and
OL,7,FFulham striker Matt Smith and Steve
OL,8,FBruce's daughter Amy, had employed Eva
OL,9,FClements through a company named
OL,10,FRuthie Maternity Services after their
OL,11,Fson had difficulties sleeping in the
OL,12,Fafternoons.
OL,14,FThey believed Ms Clements was skilled,
OL,15,Ffully trained and vetted and that the
OL,16,Fcompany was a well-established
OL,17,Fmaternity and sleep support service
OL,18,Fbut Stockport Coroner's Court heard
OL,19,Fthat neither was regulated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FMs Clements said she had a degree in
OL,7,Fearly years education but admitted she
OL,8,Fhad no medical qualifications.
OL,10,FThe inquest heard Madison's parents
OL,11,Fwould "never have dreamed" of putting
OL,12,Ftheir son asleep in the prone position
OL,13,Fbut for the advice of the maternity
OL,14,Fnurse who was said to have informed
OL,15,Fthem that all four of her own babies
OL,16,Fhad slept on their stomachs with no
OL,17,Fproblems.
OL,26,@sD@GOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FSuch advice was contrary to recognised
OL,7,Fsafe sleeping guidance from the NHS
OL,8,Fand health professionals for young
OL,9,Fbabies who cannot turn themselves over
OL,10,Fand therefore should be placed to
OL,11,Fsleep on their backs to reduce risk of
OL,12,Fa sudden and unexpected death.
OL,14,FIn a short, narrative conclusion,
OL,15,Fsenior coroner for south Manchester,
OL,16,FAlison Mutch, said: "Madison died in
OL,17,Fcircumstances where his cause of death
OL,18,Fcould not be ascertained while asleep
OL,19,Fin his cot having been placed in a
OL,20,Fprone and unsafe sleeping position."
OL,26,@xD@UOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FShe said the "purported expertise" of
OL,7,Funtrained people posed a risk to all
OL,8,Fchildren where those unregulated
OL,9,Fservices were used.
OL,11,FIssuing a prevention of future deaths
OL,12,Freport to the Secretary of State for
OL,13,FHealth, she said: "I hope the services
OL,14,Fcan be regulated and, going forward,
OL,15,Fparents are not left in a situation
OL,16,Fwhere they believe they are employing
OL,17,Fsomeone who is qualified to advise
OL,18,Fthem when they are clearly
OL,19,Funqualified."
OL,26,@nD@NOUnD@bO]uD@SOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FShe went on: "We have been told that
OL,7,Fin effect any of of us could leave the
OL,8,Fbuilding today and call ourselves a
OL,9,Fmaternity nurse as while the term
OL,10,Fregistered nurse is strictly
OL,11,Fcontrolled, the term nurse is not.
OL,13,F"It gives an illusion of someone who
OL,14,Fis highly trained and able to support
OL,15,Fparents."
OL,26,@nD@NOUuD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FShe said Ms Clements slept in a
OL,7,Fdifferent room and had responsibility
OL,8,Ffor checking on Madison but although
OL,9,Fhe was heard through a baby monitor to
OL,10,Fstir a number of times during the
OL,11,Fnight and had cried she had not gone
OL,12,Finto his nursery.
OL,14,FMadison's parents, together with Bruce
OL,15,Fand his son, ex-footballer Alex,
OL,16,Fattended Monday's hearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
