OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FFormer Manchester United player Bruce
OL,7,Fwas managing Blackpool FC at the time
OL,8,Fof the incident and missed the club's
OL,9,Ffollowing game and in a message posted
OL,10,Fon the club's official X account said:
OL,11,F"It's been the worst time of my
OL,12,Ffamily's entire lives and is something
OL,13,Fno family should have to endure."
OL,15,FIn a statement read to the court on
OL,16,FMonday, Mr Smith said the couple's son
OL,17,Fwas their "precious, perfect little
OL,18,Fboy".
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@aO]yD@KOUzD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FHe said: "Losing Madison has been
OL,7,Futterly excruciating. The pain is
OL,8,Findescribable and often too much to
OL,9,Fbear. It has totally shattered our
OL,10,Fentire family.
OL,12,F"We believe that Madison died in a
OL,13,Fcomplete regulatory vacuum. Without
OL,14,Fregulation this will happen again and
OL,15,Fother parents will place trust in
OL,16,Findividuals who should not be in the
OL,17,Fcare of infants."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
