PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FThe website of Ruthie Maternity
OL,7,FServices invites visitors to 'Hire a
OL,8,FRuthie Maternity Nurse' and 'Become a
OL,9,FRuthie Maternity Nurse".
OL,11,FRuth Asare, head of Ruthie Maternity
OL,12,FServices, said she had no medical
OL,13,Fqualifications and had only a first
OL,14,Faid certificate and a Level 2 diploma
OL,15,Fin post-natal care gained from from a
OL,16,Fthree-day course and a six-month
OL,17,Fcoursework project.
OL,26,@qD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FThe website states: "Ruthie Maternity
OL,7,FServices believe having the right
OL,8,Fmaternity nurse who understands all
OL,9,Fthe elements in caring for your baby `
OL,10,Flike feeding and sleep training whilst
OL,11,Fincorporating the right activities `
OL,12,Fwill achieve the perfect routine for
OL,13,Fyour family."
OL,15,FThe company trained individuals on one-
OL,16,Fday courses for a fee of #450, the
OL,17,Finquest heard.
OL,26,@nD@UOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FMs Asare told the coroner that those
OL,7,Fshe trained were given the safe
OL,8,Fsleeping advice to put babies on their
OL,9,Fbacks.
OL,11,FHowever, Ms Clements said she had been
OL,12,Ftaught by Ms Asare to put babies on
OL,13,Ftheir tummies.
OL,15,FShe denied telling Madison's mother
OL,16,Fshe was a nurse and also denied
OL,17,Fsuggestions she had "convinced her"
OL,18,Fthat the prone position was
OL,19,Fappropriate.
OL,26,@yD@UOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FLisa Judge, representing the boy's
OL,7,Fparents, said: "Do you remember mum's
OL,8,Flast words to you that night? That if
OL,9,Fthere was any problem whatsoever to
OL,10,Fcome and wake her up."
OL,12,FMs Clements replied: "No, I don't
OL,13,Fremember that."
OL,15,FThe court heard police conducted an
OL,16,Finvestigation and arrested Ms Clement
OL,17,Fon suspicion of neglect.
OL,26,@oD@POUrD@VO]tD@VOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774386358
OL,3,CSteve Bruce's grandson died after
OL,4,Cbeing put in 'unsafe sleeping position'
OL,6,FSenior investigating officer Det Ch
OL,7,FInsp Matthew Dixon, of Greater
OL,8,FManchester Police, said the Crown
OL,9,FProsecution Service was approached for
OL,10,Fdirections and guidance, and it was
OL,11,Fidentified that the criminal threshold
OL,12,Fhad not been met.
OL,14,FHe said this was mainly because of the
OL,15,Funregulation of such maternity
OL,16,Fservices and that it was not illegal
OL,17,Fto place a baby on its front.
OL,19,FHe added it could not be determined
OL,20,Fthat Ms Clements set out to wilfully
OL,21,Fharm Madison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
